urdu transliteration text:
Lori Suna Rahi HunI AM SINGING A LULLABY English Transliteration
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Mujhko Yahi Khabar Hai Dukh Dard Ki Ho MaariTumko Hai Sabr Karna Ye Bhi Khuda Ki MarziTu Misle Fatema Ab Banna Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Ayega Ab Na Koi Bhi Leke TaziyaneMarega Na Shimar Ab Rukhsar Par TamacheHar Aik Saans Pe Na Ghabra Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Kuchh Din Me To Rihayi Miljayegi SakinaZindane Gham Se Chhutke Jayege Hum MadinaMadar Ye Kar Rahi Hai Wada Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Jab Neend Agayi Thi, Phir Khaab Aayi HaayeJis Mei Hussain Apni Beti Se Keh Rahe TheAb Waqt Agaya Hai Aja Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Jab Qaid Me Sakina Ko Maut Agayi ThiBazu Hila Hila Ke Madar Ye Roke BoliMujhse Khata Huwi Kya Batla Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Abid Larazte Hathon Se Ik Lahad BanayeYe Kehke Apni Behna Ko Phir Wahi LitaayeKaise Sahunga Me Gham Tera Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme

Paye The Jab Rihayi, Ehle Haram “Tejani”Banu Sisak Sisak Ke Girkar Yahi PukariKaise Watan Ko Jaun Tanha Meri Sakina
@HujjatELC
Lori Suna Rahi Hun- I am telling a bedtime rhyme
